# Fincore

Fincore is a modern financial management platform.

## Goals

- Learn and apply modern software architecture
- Build a scalable financial application
- Use Clean Architecture principles
- Create production-ready mobile and backend systems

## Technology Stack

### Mobile
- Flutter
- Riverpod
- Material 3

### Backend
- .NET
- Clean Architecture
- PostgreSQL / SQL Server

## Architecture

The project follows:

- Clean Architecture
- SOLID principles
- Domain Driven Design concepts
- Dependency Inversion

## Development Environment

- Ubuntu WSL
- VS Code
- GitHub
- Flutter SDK
